edu.nd.darts.cimon
Class EventList

java.lang.Object
  edu.nd.darts.cimon.EventList

public final class EventList
extends Object

Maintains static list of all active event notification monitors and conditional monitors. Each event notification monitor and conditional monitor is represented by a ConditionTree.

Author:
darts

getEvent

public ConditionTree getEvent(int monitorId)
Get ConditionTree which matches callback. Returns ConditionTree representing an active event notification monitor or conditional monitor. _callback_ should be the Messenger or PendingIntent that was used to register the event notification/conditional monitor (or a Callback encapsulating this).

Parameters:
monitorId - unique id of this event notification or conditional monitor
Returns:
ConditionTree representing event notification or conditional monitor
See Also:
ConditionTree, Callback

insertEvent

public void insertEvent(ConditionTree event)
Insert new conditional monitor or event notification monitor into list of active event monitors.

Parameters:
event - new ConditionTree representing event notification or conditional monitor

removeEvent

public void removeEvent(ConditionTree event)
Remove conditional monitor or event notification monitor from list of active event monitors. This posts runnable to thread which calls on private method (to ensure thread synchronization).

Parameters:
event - ConditionTree representing event notification or conditional monitor to be removed

_removeEvent

private boolean _removeEvent(ConditionTree event)
Removes conditional monitor or event notification monitor from list.

Parameters:

Returns:
true if removal was successful
